ugin that should have done the same but it kept forgetting the order and also the posts weren\'t displayed in their categories which was more difficult to visualise the order. </div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Banner on WP Doesn&#039;t Go Away</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/newyorkedge"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25bf1aa12409d52d4be518c5dc02a84f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25bf1aa12409d52d4be518c5dc02a84f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/newyorkedge" class="reviewer-name">newyorkedge</a> le <span class="review-date">septembre 1, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Even after leaving a review the banner on my WP does not go away.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">One of my default plugin</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mandipluitel"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5291983bbaf0b3e31c6aa2d0aa9fa6e5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5291983bbaf0b3e31c6aa2d0aa9fa6e5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mandipluitel" class="reviewer-name">mandipluitel</a> le <span class="review-date">août 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Thanks for having all the features that I always wanted :)</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">I Like this Plugin</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/margonfil"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/31d3bb93659d721db937beed08726e6a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/31d3bb93659d721db937beed08726e6a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/margonf